description: Philippines: Capacity Building to Remove Barriers to Renewable Energy Development

subproject.description: The project will implement: (1) National renewable energy(NRE) policy, planning and institutional capacity building; (2) NRE market services institutionalization; (3) NRE information and Promotion Services; (4) NRE initiatives delivery and financing mechanisms; (5)NRE training program and (6) NRE technology support .
